quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,6,"Indeed, those who disbelieve{1} - it is all the same for them whether you warn them or do not warn them - they will not believe.",footnotes:1:1
  2,7,"Allāh has set a seal upon their hearts and upon their hearing, and over their vision is a veil.{1} And for them is a great punishment.",footnotes:1:1
  2,8,"And of the people are some who say, "We believe in Allāh and the Last Day," but they are not believers."
  2,9,"They [think to] deceive Allāh and those who believe, but they deceive not except themselves and perceive [it] not."
  2,10,"In their hearts is disease, so Allāh has increased their disease;{1} and for them is a painful punishment because they [habitually] used to lie.",footnotes:1:1